snippet.title: FatalClaw Trailer
snippet.description:
FatalClaw is a high-quality 2D Metroidvania game.
Explore the mysterious underworld in your own way with cat “Kisha” who rise from the dead, and find the key to the ground with other survivors through absorbing the power infected enemies.
